window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This is the sixth audiobook in the Billionaire's Ultimatum series. </p> <p>After Solomon Royce's untoward advances and Beatrice Landseer's initial harassment, nothing can get worse for Jessika, right? Unfortunately, no, it's not that simple. </p> <p>When Beatrice berates Jessika's life, personality, and family, Jessika realizes this was a mistake. Agreeing to help billionaire CEO Asher Landseer with his hopes and dreams will only end in grief. But, still, is it possible to stop now? Jessika knows it is, knows she should, but whenever Asher smiles - at her and only her - she becomes resolute. </p> <p>Will the reward outweigh the risk, though? Is there any reward to begin with? Is Asher's controlling, dominant personality too much for Jessika to handle? Or is it exactly what she needs and wants? When he surprises her, visiting in the middle of the night, they both realize just how far they're willing to go for a glimpse of happiness. </p> <p>Little does either of them realize, there's collusion and treachery surrounding them that could come crashing down at any moment and ruin their chances at everything. </p> <p><b>NOTE</b>: This seductive contemporary BDSM erotic romance audiobook contains themes of domination and submission. </p>"; 
